            </div>
            <div class="poznamka-item">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
              <p><strong>Príslušenstvo:</strong> Ku tomuto produktu si môžete zakúpiť vrtáky priamo na našej prevádzke za výhodné ceny.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Technické parametre -->
      <div class="technicke-parametre">
        <h2>Technické parametre</h2>
        <div class="parametre-grid">
          <div class="parameter-item">
            <span class="parameter-label">Príkon:</span>
            <span class="parameter-value">450W</span>
          </div>
          <div class="parameter-item">
            <span class="parameter-label">Voľnobežné otáčky:</span>
            <span class="parameter-value">0 - 3400 min⁻¹</span>
          </div>
          <div class="parameter-item">
            <span class="parameter-label">Upínací rozsah skľučovadla:</span>
            <span class="parameter-value">1.5 - 10 mm</span>
          </div>
          <div class="parameter-item">
            <span class="parameter-label">Max. vŕtací výkon - oceľ:</span>
            <span class="parameter-value">10 mm</span>
          </div>
          <div class="parameter-item">
            <span class="parameter-label">Max. vŕtací výkon - drevo:</span>
            <span class="parameter-value">25 mm</span>
          </div>
          <div class="parameter-item highlight-param">
            <span class="parameter-label">Hmotnosť:</span>
            <span class="parameter-value">1.3 kg</span>
          </div>
          <div class="parameter-item">
            <span class="parameter-label">Rozmery (D x Š x V):</span>
            <span class="parameter-value">234 x 64 x 183 mm</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Vlastnosti -->
      <div class="vlastnosti-section">
        <h2>Vlastnosti a výhody</h2>
        <ul class="vlastnosti-list">
          <li>Praktický a ľahký nástroj pri výkonnom motore 450 W</li>
          <li>Pružnočný dizajn prenáša tak vŕtanie do strediska bez vŕtačky</li>
          <li>Zmena otáčania dopredačky/dozadu s elektronickým ovládaním a aretačným tlačidlom pre neprerušenú prevádzku</li>
          <li>Rýchloupínacie skľučovadlo</li>
          <li>Konštrukcia s guľôčkovými ložiskami umožňuje presné vŕtanie a skrutkovanie</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA sekcia -->
      <div class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Pripravený na rezerváciu?</h2>
          <p>Kontaktujte nás pre rezerváciu alebo ďalšie informácie o Makita 6413</p>
          <div class="cta-actions">
            <a 
              href="mailto:info@royalstroje.sk?subject=Rezervácia Makita 6413&body=Dobrý deň,%0A%0Achcem si rezervovať Makita 6413%0A%0ATermín prenájmu:%0AOd:%0ADo:%0A%0AMeno:%0ATelefón:"
              class="cta-email"
            >
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M20 4H4C2.9 4 2.01 4.9 2.01 6L2 18C2 19.1 2.9 20 4 20H20C21.1 20 22 19.1 22 18V6C22 4.9 21.1 4 20 4ZM20 8L12 13L4 8V6L12 11L20 6V8Z"/>
              </svg>
              Rezervovať emailom
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+421948555551" class="cta-phone">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M6.62 10.79a15.05 15.05 0 006.59 6.59l2.2-2.2a1 1 0 011.01-.24c1.11.37 2.31.57 3.58.57a1 1 0 011 1v3.5a1 1 0 01-1 1C12.4 21.82 2.18 11.6 2.18 3a1 1 0 011-1H6.7a1 1 0 011 1c0 1.27.2 2.47.57 3.58a1 1 0 01-.24 1.01l-2.2 2.2z"/>
              </svg>
              Zavolajte 0948 555 551
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --brand: #f66000;
    --brand-light: #ff8533;
    --brand-dark: #e85d00;
    --text: #ffffff;
    --text-dim: #b0b0b0;
    --bg: #0a0a0a;
    --bg-secondary: #111111;
  }

  /* PRODUKT DETAIL SECTION */
  .produkt-detail-section {
    padding: 40px 0 120px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a0a 0%, #111111 50%, #0a0a0a 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
  }

  .produkt-detail-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .produkt-detail-section::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1) 1px, transparent 0);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
    opacity: 0.2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* BREADCRUMBS */
  .breadcrumbs {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .breadcrumbs ol {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .breadcrumbs li:not(:last-child)::after {
    content: '>';
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: var(--brand);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .breadcrumbs a:hover {
    color: var(--brand-light);
  }

  .breadcrumbs li[aria-current="page"] {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* PRODUKT HERO */
  .produkt-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .produkt-obrazok {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 400px;
  }

  .produkt-obrazok img {
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .produkt-info {
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .produkt-badge {
    background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
    color: var(--brand);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .produkt-nazov {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .produkt-typ {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--brand);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .produkt-highlights {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .highlight-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .highlight-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .highlight-label {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .highlight-value {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .highlight-weight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.15), rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.08));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.25);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .highlight-price {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-light));
    color: #000;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .produkt-akcie {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .rezervovat-btn-primary {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-light));
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .rezervovat-btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 35px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .rezervovat-btn-primary svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .zavolat-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--brand);
    color: var(--brand);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .zavolat-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .zavolat-btn svg {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  /* CENNÍK A INFORMÁCIE */
  .cennik-section {
    background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .cennik-section h2 {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cennik-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cennik-hlavny {
    background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cena-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cena-label {
    display: block;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .cena-hodnota {
    display: block;
    color: var(--brand);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .cena-hodnota.kaucia {
    color: #ff4444;
  }

  .cennik-poznamky {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .poznamka-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .poznamka-item svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    fill: var(--brand);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .poznamka-item p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .poznamka-item strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* TECHNICKÉ PARAMETRE */
  .technicke-parametre {
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .technicke-parametre h2 {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .parametre-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px;
  }

  .parameter-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .parameter-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .parameter-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .parameter-value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .highlight-param .parameter-value {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.15), rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.08));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.25);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  /* VLASTNOSTI */
  .vlastnosti-section {
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .vlastnosti-section h2 {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .vlastnosti-list {
    background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.8);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px;
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .vlastnosti-list li {
    padding: 16px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 32px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .vlastnosti-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .vlastnosti-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--brand);
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  /* CTA SECTION */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1), rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.05));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-email,
  .cta-phone {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-email {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-light));
    color: #000;
  }

  .cta-phone {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--brand);
    color: var(--brand);
  }

  .cta-email:hover,
  .cta-phone:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .cta-phone:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 107, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .cta-email svg,
  .cta-phone svg {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .produkt-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
